    <item>
      <title>美联储降息前景导致股市和债市回落：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五非农就业数据公布后，交易员削减对美联储降息的押注，欧洲股市和美国股指期货下跌。全球债券收益率上升，美元走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 22:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑交易员已准备好在抛售后再次下跌 8%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/pound-traders-are-ready-for-another-8-slump-after-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期权市场的交易员们正在为英镑进一步下跌 8% 做准备，因为财政问题引发了上周英国股市的惨痛抛售，给英镑造成了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/pound-traders-are-ready-for-another-8-slump-after-market-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
